    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I cannot tell how silently He suffered,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As with His peace He graced this place of tears,"
