          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How He will claim His earthly heritage,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How satisfy the needs and aspirations"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Of east and west, of sinner and of sage."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But this I know, all flesh shall see His glory,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And He shall reap the harvest He has sown,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And some glad day His sun shall shine in splendor"
